   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00032"/><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb235251"><hi rend="latintype">Hasenauerstr</hi> 59</rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00031"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb723" type="place">Wildbad Waldbrunn</rs> bei <rs ref="#pmb428" type="place">Welsberg</rs> im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb724">Pustertale</rs>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00032"/><date when="1907-08-19">19. 8. 907</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>lieber Richard;</salute> wir bleiben hier bis <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01700-1"/><date>26.</date>
               (<date>27.</date>. <date>28</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01700-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> hielt sich noch bis <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1907-08-26" subtype="date-only"/> im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb723">Wildbad Waldbrunn</rs> auf.</note>)?; (<date>Donner<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date> ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>t vielleicht <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01700-2"/><rs ref="#pmb11485" type="person">Goldmann</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01700-2">Zu einem Zusammentreffen
                  mit <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Goldmann</rs> kam es nicht, <ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L01702" subtype="cf"/>.</note>) da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb40120" type="place">Dolomiten<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>traße</rs> (wahr<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinlich <rs ref="#pmb40350" type="place">Grödner Thal</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40346" type="place">Grödner Joch</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><supplied>–</supplied><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb40369" type="place">Pordoj</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40362" type="place">Vigo</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40371" type="place">Karer<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs>, – <rs ref="#pmb40260" type="place">Bozen</rs>.) da<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb43520" type="place">Meran</rs>, eventuell <rs ref="#pmb39975" type="place">Garda<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs>, zurück zwi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen <date>5</date> u. <date>10</date>, mit
               event. Aufenthalt (<rs ref="#pmb867" type="place">I<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>sbruck</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs>.) Auf Wieder<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen
               hoffentlich.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer><postscript><p>Schreiben Sie ein Wort! Viele Grüße über die Lande.</p></postscript></div>
      </body>
